<h1 id="cack">CacÄ±k</h1>

<h4 id="mint-yogurt-cucumber-and-garlic-salad">Mint, yogurt, cucumber and garlic salad.</h4>

<ul>
  <li>2 Garlic cloves <em>finely chopped or blended</em></li>
  <li>Over 300 ml of yogurt</li>
  <li>Half a decent sized cucumber <em>finely chopped</em></li>
  <li>Good handful of mint leaves <em>blended or very finely chopped</em></li>
  <li>Salt</li>
  <li>2 tbsp water</li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>If you have a blender, blend 1/2 tbsp yogurt with the mint and garlic.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Combine the yogurt, mint and garlic - mix well. Add more water if it seems
too thick.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Add the cucumber and mix well.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
